| Next.js project setup | web/ | App Router, TailwindCSS, NextAuth |
| Auth flow | web/app/api/auth/ | Google OAuth login |
| Submit page | web/app/(app)/submit/ | Drag-drop upload + live AI detection stream |
| Detection animation | web/components/app/DetectionStream.tsx | Step-by-step pipeline visualization |
| Price comparison widget | web/components/app/PriceComparison.tsx | Live cost comparison vs Colab/AWS |
| Monitor page | web/app/(app)/monitor/ | Live chunk cards with GPU bars |
| Results page | web/app/(app)/results/ | Download, video preview, training curves |
| WebSocket integration | web/lib/ws.ts | Real-time updates hook |
| **Testable outcome:** | | Full user flow: login → upload → watch detection → monitor chunks → download results |

